### HOW TO MAKE A RELEASE

Prepare build packages:
* pip install build
* pip install twine

* Add changes to `CHANGELOG.md`
* Change version in `iban_oplata/__init__.py` and `pyproject.toml`
* `source .env/bin/activate`
* `python3 -m build --sdist --wheel`
* `twine upload dist/*`
